OL,3,CPope says he shares suffering of all
OL,4,Csick people as he recovers from
OL,5,Cpneumonia
OL,7,FPope Francis has said he shares the
OL,8,Fsuffering of all sick people and
OL,9,Fprayed again for peace in Ukraine and
OL,10,Felsewhere while he recovers from
OL,11,Fdouble pneumonia.
OL,13,FThe Pope had a peaceful night and is
OL,14,Fresting after a bronchial spasm caused
OL,15,Fhim to inhale vomit, requiring non-
OL,16,Finvasive ventilation on Friday. He has
OL,17,Fbeen battling pneumonia for two weeks.
