OL,3,CPope says he shares suffering of all
OL,4,Csick people as he recovers from
OL,5,Cpneumonia
OL,7,FThe Vatican shared a message from the
OL,8,Fpope on Sunday in which he thanked his
OL,9,Fdoctors for their care and well-
OL,10,Fwishers for their prayers.
OL,12,F"From here, war appears even more
OL,13,Fabsurd," Francis said in the message,
OL,14,Fwhich he drafted in recent days from
OL,15,Fthe Gemelli hospital.
OL,17,FHe added that his time in hospital was
OL,18,Fa moment of deep solidarity with those
OL,19,Fwho are sick and suffering worldwide.
