OL,3,CPope says he shares suffering of all
OL,4,Csick people as he recovers from
OL,5,Cpneumonia
OL,7,F"I feel in my heart the 'blessing'
OL,8,Fthat is hidden within frailty, because
OL,9,Fit is precisely in these moments that
OL,10,Fwe learn even more to trust in the
OL,11,FLord," he said.
OL,13,F"At the same time, I thank God for
OL,14,Fgiving me the opportunity to share in
OL,15,Fbody and spirit the condition of so
OL,16,Fmany sick and suffering people."
OL,18,FIt was the third consecutive weekend
OL,19,Fthat Francis had missed delivering the
OL,20,FSunday Angelus prayer in person.
