OL,7,FHe has no fever or signs of elevated
OL,8,Fwhite blood cells, which would signal
OL,9,Fhis body was still fighting an
OL,10,Finfection.
OL,12,FDoctors on Saturday reported that
OL,13,FFrancis was in stable condition, with
OL,14,Fno mention of him being critical.
OL,16,FThis is his fourth hospitalisation
OL,17,Fsince his 2013 election, raising
OL,18,Fconcerns about his increasingly
OL,19,Ffragile health.
