OL,7,FFrancis has other health problems as
OL,8,Fwell. He uses a wheelchair, walker, or
OL,9,Fcane to move around his apartment and
OL,10,Frecently fell twice, injuring his arm
OL,11,Fand chin.
OL,13,FIn 2021, he had 33cm of his large
OL,14,Fintestine removed due to a narrowing
OL,15,Fof the colon. Two years later, he
OL,16,Funderwent further abdominal surgery to
OL,17,Fremove scar tissue and repair a hernia.
