OL,7,FDuring a 2023 hospital stay, he was
OL,8,Fdiagnosed with what he later described
OL,9,Fas "acute and strong pneumonia in the
OL,10,Flower part of the lungs".
OL,12,FBronchitis can sometimes develop into
OL,13,Fpneumonia, a more severe infection
OL,14,Faffecting the lungs' air sacs.
